{
  "user_schedule": {
    "day": 1,
    "早晨": "去上课，中间去拿了联动外卖",
    "中午": "睡午觉，去上下午的课",
    "下午": "上课，上课时看视频。",
    "晚上": "去机械创新实验室值班",
    "夜晚": "回宿舍晾了衣服睡觉"
  },
  "history": "",
  "relationship": "Two people have just met and are still unfamiliar with each other. Their conversations are mostly polite and superficial, limited to everyday topics like work, studies, or the weather. At this stage, both sides are cautious and have yet to reveal their true selves.",
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "content": "[震惊.jpg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我知道这问题很冒昧。可是您是什么人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "当我是普通网友好了。你会以为我是什么人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "07:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "[摇晃酒杯.jpg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka"
    },
    {
      "content": "这看起来一点也不普通，太神秘了。您究竟是我的导员、诈骗犯还是什么贵人？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:48",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "……？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "07:48",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "[疑惑.jpg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "07:48",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "[喝茶.jpg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "07:49",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "也许是我宿舍摆的小人太多了中了邪……或者我发烧烧迷糊了。您想要什么",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:49",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你应该吃点药",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "07:49",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "是啊，我弄丢了。不大想找…… ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:50",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "[无奈.jpg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "07:50",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你多大了？你家大人会担心的。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka"
    },
    {
      "content": "我还不知道你是谁呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:50",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "等等，我先不和你说了，要迟到了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:51",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我曾经听说有人感冒的时候运动得心肌炎死掉了。可是我不跑就赶不上上课铃，说不定我也要死了，我就说都怪学校。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:51",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "[叹气.jpg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "07:51",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不能请假么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "07:51",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "请不了。请假也算未出勤，也扣平时分的。不管我们是生病了还是死了，没去就扣平时分。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:51",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "这课重要么？不重要的话睡一会吧。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "07:52",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯……",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:52",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不过你到底是谁啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:52",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "[揉眼睛.pg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:53",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "这种问题的答案，除了不重要就是不告诉你。为什么还要问呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "07:53",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "[哼歌.jpg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka"
    },
    {
      "content": "况且就算是现实中“认识”的人，也总是没法证明你真的足够了解、以至于可以称为“认识”他本人……",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "07:53",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "所以就没什么关系了，如我所说，当作普通网友就好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka"
    },
    {
      "content": "[摇晃酒杯.jpg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "07:54",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "……我了个长难句啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:54",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "[短路.jpg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:54",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "唔……您有什么好看的电影推荐吗。我找半天了，也没看到合适的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:23",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "影视作品就像是让人体验了另一种社会、另一种人生一样",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:23",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "您说我这么年轻，却被关在学校里，学没有用的东西……可能是我的心态有问题，可是我觉得在这里的生活像一片空白似的。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "匹诺康尼的影业足够发达，也许你可以试试芮克导演的作品。他的选题有时……微妙的很特别。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "14:24",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "如果你愿意听我的建议，这种时候最重要的是确定下一步的方向。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka"
    },
    {
      "content": "不过人生且长……如果可以的话，好好地去“体验”些什么也很有意义",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka"
    },
    {
      "content": "[摇尾巴jpg.]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:24",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我可以问您参加工作多久了吗？因为……如果工作以后的生活还不如上学的话，岂不是太没盼头了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:24",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "这个啊……很长时间了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "14:25",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我的感受……谈不上喜欢这份工作，但当然不是讨厌。我更倾向于它属于所谓命运，所以无论遇到好事还是坏事，也就坦然了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "14:25",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "您会说“工作了就知道上学轻松了”这种话吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:25",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不会，我也不建议你相信。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "14:26",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "许多人都在背叛自己。他们否认曾经处境里的痛苦，只是为了夸大现在遭逢的苦难",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "14:26",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "对于他们来说，只有自己正处于的时期才是最苦的，既否认了其余所有人，也背叛了以前的自己。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka"
    },
    {
      "content": "比如，你会觉得上幼儿园的时候最轻松吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "14:26",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不会。我的饮食起居和日常活动都被管控，我抗拒睡午觉、不被允许吃各种零食，不能随便买玩具",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:27",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "幼儿园的时候我也一样的不愿上学，还会因对父母的依赖而对父母终将死去这件事产生极大的恐惧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以我可以确定，我从不觉得自己幼儿园的时候比现在更轻松。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯哼，这些都是合理的。但是许多人一定会说:当然是幼儿园最轻松了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "14:27",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "他们有理有据地就条件夸夸其谈……根据他们此刻的衡量标准。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "14:27",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "从某种意义上而言，当时的他们已经不存在了，也无法反驳。他们把过去的自己忘记了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka"
    },
    {
      "role": "User",
      "content": "[思索.jpg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01
    },
    {
      "content": "简而言之，可以说每个时期的经历造就了后来的我们，忘记与否认过去，都会让人容易迷失自我的。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "14:28",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "嘶……我从来没听人说过您这样的话。以前一直觉得有什么不对，可是我说不清楚……总而言之，谢谢您！！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:28",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "没关系。要记得，让自己幸福是生命的第一要务。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka",
      "timestamp": "14:28",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "[哼歌.jpg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kafka"
    }
  ],
